						<summary>

						<p>It records the gift of the village Tirumukkūḍal, as <hi rend="italic">sarvamāṉya</hi> and also the assignment of taxes such as <hi rend="italic">iḍaiturai, āḷamañji</hi> etc., to the temple of Śrī Veṅkaṭēsvarasvāmi by Veṅkaṭappa-Nāyaka, according to an order issued by Rāmapaiyar at the instance of Doḍḍayarasar.</p>						

